 蜀道難</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%AB-T%C3%A1i-T%C6%B0/Thu%E1%BB%B7-ti%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%AD-D%E1%BA%A1-v%C5%A9/poem-LDPJQhRgiMBc0ecA0f9JFA">Thuỷ tiên tử - Dạ vũ - 水仙子－夜雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%AB-T%C3%A1i-T%C6%B0/author-msizrmP9r6u-7dxWcXZWeg">Trừ Tái Tư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Ng%C3%B4-S%C3%B4/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD-T%C3%A2y-Thi/poem-ViRbvDF0HhDrI49XK06Txg">Vịnh sử - Tây Thi - 詠史－西施</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Ng%C3%B4-S%C3%B4/author-U-Qw0U7nLVKqm8kibmDN6g">Hà Ngô Sô</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/Y%C3%AAn-ca-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-2-Bi%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-Kc8R88uruzsjyzzUopw4VQ">Yên ca hành kỳ 2 - Biệt nhật - 燕歌行其二－別日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/author-_plJ3nwj8cVN02KPZ4P_8g">Tào Phi</a>)<br></div>	</div>
